Package: FlowCodeUnmix
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Unmixing FlowCode Spectral Cytometry Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Oliver", "Burton",
      email = "olivertburton@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Add on package to AutoSpectral to support unmixing and debarcoding
    of spectral flow cytometry files from experiments using FlowCode or ProCode
    technology. Provides per-cell unmixing optimization to account for FRET
    between fluorescent antibody conjugates binding to proximal epitope tags.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
